### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific restaurant's menu
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/5

### Get a specific user by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/name/Diana

### Create a new menu item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 22,
  "name": "Giselle",
  "surname1": "Mendiola",
  "surname2": "Romero",
  "email": "miss.u@heart.com",
  "password": "2208",
  "phoneNumber": "7295031567",
  "userType": "CUSTOMER",
  "rate": 5
}

### Update an existing user
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5,
  "name": "Giselle",
  "surname1": "Mendiola",
  "surname2": "Romero",
  "email": "miss.u@heart.com",
  "password": "2208",
  "phoneNumber": "7295031567",
  "userType": "CUSTOMER",
  "rate": 4
}

### Delete a user by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/2
Content-Type: application/json